---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import founderImage from "../assets/images/ray_avatar.png";
---

<section class="about-ray-section" id="over">
  <div class="about-ray-inner">

    <div class="about-ray-image-wrap">
      <Image
        class="about-ray-image"
        src={founderImage}
        alt="Ray – oprichter van LuminX"
        widths={[420, 640, 920]}
        sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 48vw"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="about-ray-content">
      <span class="about-ray-kicker">Over mij</span>
      <h2>Geen bureau-constructie.<br/>Gewoon directe samenwerking.</h2>
      <p>
        Ik ben Ray, oprichter van LuminX. Met een achtergrond in Senior Online Marketing, Development, Marketing automation en strategie help ik
        ondernemers om slimmer te werken en online te groeien. Je werkt rechtstreeks met mij, niet met
        een accountmanager die het daarna doorgeeft.
      </p>
      <p>
        Van procesautomatisering tot paid campagnes: ik kijk altijd naar het grotere plaatje en vertaal dat
        naar oplossingen die vandaag werken én morgen meeschalen.
      </p>
      <div class="about-ray-actions">
        <a href="#" class="about-ray-cta" data-overlay-open>Plan een kennismaking</a>
        <a href="tel:+31613698596" class="about-ray-phone">+31 6 1369 8596</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-ray-section {
    padding: 7rem 4rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(10,10,10,0.07);
  }

  .about-ray-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-ray-image-wrap {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-ray-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-ray-kicker {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.42;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .about-ray-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-ray-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(10,10,10,0.62);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-ray-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }

  .about-ray-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease;
  }
  .about-ray-cta:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

  .about-ray-phone {
    color: var(--black);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.45;
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
  }
  .about-ray-phone:hover { opacity: 1; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-ray-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .about-ray-image-wrap {
      max-width: 420px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-ray-section {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
